{"tid":480051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"叫雞就叫雞啦 咩心地善良","createTime":"2017-11-25T17:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T08:02:29.000Z","uid":88888,"like":54,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8b772699aa3d02d11c7104cd4d3f43fd5cef98d3","tid":480051,"uid":88888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:09:28.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post 話叫雞嘅人係心地善良，仲要好多人正評咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞蟲叫雞其實只係為滿足自己性慾，有買有賣，你俾錢換服務唔係問題，但憑咩美化呢個行為做心地善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個堆雞多數都係為咗唔洗用腦去賺快錢就擺個西出黎賣，隔離post 就ff到人地逼不得已/唔做雞就無錢開飯咁，美化自己俾錢叫雞就係解救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係個句叫雞唔係問題，向好個方面諗可以減少人呃蝦條又或者非禮強姦個啲嘅。乜鳩 叫雞嘅人係心地善良 ，你咸濕就咸濕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預咗俾一眾偉大嘅雞蟲負皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b329eb2f44c9fe3f23d6231285e1f101736383","tid":480051,"uid":19502,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"雞蟲善良 人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9e40cb478c05224b8492899dd7b4c68108d5ae","tid":480051,"uid":7837,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:13:22.000Z","msg":"上連登勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12ad7446a09766103ff2a0d8577facadd8373a9","tid":480051,"uid":88888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上連登勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺認真咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a533c94f0a66a73276a5173821f46903411cc11a","tid":480051,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T19:48:35.000Z","msg":"大波妹先心地善良"},{"pid":"6dd0b37c2afdfe630b53aee43ede18aa755aa6a9","tid":480051,"uid":88888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大波妹先心地善良</blockquote><br />\n你啱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa07106ee5ae953a3a5b45bbf2af46840f896a7","tid":480051,"uid":139613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:46:03.000Z","msg":"我最善良"},{"pid":"658fda803cb6abeb469580cf7e9591d6cf30802a","tid":480051,"uid":1997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"擺到明9UP POST都咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41239fbd15b2fede8c605dfeb3c4e2201e36bca","tid":480051,"uid":33886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"真心膠都咁多正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7201c3855df8d6bfd4331ef7d5842c396561595","tid":480051,"uid":58254,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:48:52.000Z","msg":"認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d360ab012de420e92e9fbe7fc0d28c88d160e68","tid":480051,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"ON9仔"},{"pid":"104fd223d6615885981c057e933143605bbef823","tid":480051,"uid":33886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}